00:11:08,561 --> 00:11:11,981
给 喝点 糖水可以压惊
Here, take this. The sugar will take the edge off the shock.

156
00:11:12,147 --> 00:11:14,399
来 来 再喝点
Come on, come on, drink some more.

157
00:11:23,618 --> 00:11:25,410
好了 没事了 你安全了
It's okay. It's okay. You're safe.

158
00:11:31,333 --> 00:11:32,918
你现在很安全
You're safe now.

159
00:11:35,337 --> 00:11:36,589
伯尼
Bernie.

160
00:11:36,756 --> 00:11:38,716
凯西 兰博
Casey. Rambo.

161
00:11:39,675 --> 00:11:42,261
认真点 布莱 你该考虑下加入我们
Seriously, Bry, you should think about coming with us.

162
00:11:42,427 --> 00:11:45,014
你已尝到甜头了 你还可以拿到更多
You've got the edge. There's more of this to be had.

163
00:11:45,180 --> 00:11:47,099
- 她明年要上大学了吧? - 是的
- She's going to college next year? - Yep.

164
00:11:47,266 --> 00:11:50,352
- 你就要失去她了 - 一年够我找回她了
- You're gonna lose her. - That gives me a year to find her.

165
00:11:51,103 --> 00:11:53,939
米尔斯先生 她想要见你
Mr. Mills, she'd like to see you.

166
00:11:59,236 --> 00:12:02,031
- 好点了吗? - 好多了
- How are you feeling? - Better.

167
00:12:04,784 --> 00:12:06,619
你的女儿想当歌手?
So your daughter wants to be a singer?

168
00:12:08,245 --> 00:12:09,914
是啊 从她5岁起
Yep, since she was 5.

169
00:12:10,080 --> 00:12:11,874
歌手的生活并不如其他人所想的那样
It's not what everyone thinks it is.

170
00:12:12,041 --> 00:12:17,254
一旦没了新鲜感 就只剩下酒店和机场的东奔西跑
Once the glam wears off, it's just a lot of hotel rooms, lots of airports.

171
00:12:17,797 --> 00:12:18,923
她要的就是这个
It's what she wants.

172
00:12:22,968 --> 00:12:25,137
第一个号码是我的声乐老师吉奥的
The first number is Gio, my vocal coach.

173
00:12:25,304 --> 00:12:27,306
如果他说行 就代表她能唱
If he says she can sing, she can sing.

174
00:12:27,473 --> 00:12:30,059
他会给她必要的指导 学费我来
He'll give her coaching she needs, the fee is on me.

175
00:12:30,225 --> 00:12:32,186
第二个号码是我经纪人的
The second number is my manager.

176
00:12:32,352 --> 00:12:34,939
如果吉奥肯定了她 他就能为她创造机会
If Gio clears her, he'll make sure she gets a shot.

177
00:12:36,899 --> 00:12:41,236
- 谢谢 - 不 米尔斯先生 是我要谢谢你
- Thank you. - No, Mr. Mills, thank you.

178
00:12:57,587 --> 00:12:59,755
- 她来了 - 爸爸
- There she is. - Dad.

179
00:13:02,842 --> 00:13:04,719
- 嗨 宝贝 - 嗨
- Hi, sweetie. - Hey.

180
00:13:05,260 --> 00:13:07,137
- 你好 - 你好
- Hi. - Hi.

181
00:13:07,304 --> 00:13:08,723
不要那么激动
Don't look so excited.

182
00:13:08,889 --> 00:13:12,309
我只是很惊讶 我以为就我和金米
I was just surprised. I thought it was just gonna be Kim and I.

183
00:13:12,852 --> 00:13:14,103
我叫妈妈来的
I asked Mom to come.

184
00:13:16,146 --> 00:13:19,859
一份覆盆子香蕉奶昔加樱桃 你最喜欢的
One raspberry-banana milkshake, extra cherries, just the way you like it.

185
00:13:20,067 --> 00:13:21,486
- 谢谢 - 列尼...勒诺
- Thanks. - Lennie... Lenore.

186
00:13:21,652 --> 00:13:24,363
- 你要点什么? - 不了 谢谢
- Would you like something? - I'm fine, thanks.

187
00:13:24,864 --> 00:13:26,365
那么?
So?

188
00:13:26,949 --> 00:13:28,408
爸爸 你猜怎么着
So, Dad, guess what.

189
00:13:28,576 --> 00:13:30,202
- 你知道我朋友阿曼达吧? - 嗯
- You know my friend Amanda? - Yep.

190
00:13:31,036 --> 00:13:34,039
她的表姐妹邀请我们一起去巴黎度假
Her cousins asked us to spend vacation with them in Paris.

191
00:13:34,248 --> 00:13:35,290
很酷吧?
How cool is that?

192
00:13:35,458 --> 00:13:38,002
- 你怎么想去巴黎了? - 爸爸 不会吧?
- Why do you want to go to Paris? - Dad. Hello?

193
00:13:38,168 --> 00:13:41,464
罗浮宫 印象派博物馆 毕加索博物馆
The Louvre, the lmpressionist museum, the Picasso Museum.

194
00:13:41,631 --> 00:13:43,508
我不知道你会对艺术这么感兴趣
I didn't know you were so into art.

195
00:13:43,674 --> 00:13:46,719
真的假的? 我都去过现代艺术博物馆一百多次了
Are you kidding? I've been to the MOMA, like, a hundred times.

196
00:13:46,886 --> 00:13:51,641
阿曼达去年夏天去的 回来后她都能说法语了
Amanda went last summer, she came back, she could practically speak French.

197
00:13:54,059 --> 00:13:55,520
因为你还未满18岁...
And because you're under 18...

198
00:13:55,686 --> 00:13:58,523
...所以你要得到我的允许才能出国?
...you need my permission to leave the country?

199
00:13:59,106 --> 00:14:02,527
爸爸 求你了 我真的真的很想去
Dad, please. I really, really wanna go.

200
00:14:02,693 --> 00:14:05,530
她们的公寓超棒的 可以俯瞰塞纳河
They've got this sick apartment overlooking the river.

201
00:14:05,696 --> 00:14:08,157
- 就你和阿曼达? - 还有她的表姐妹
- Just you and Amanda? - And her cousins.

202
00:14:08,323 --> 00:14:11,577
别小题大作了 布莱恩 签字吧
Don't make a big deal out of this, Bryan. Just sign the paper.

203
00:14:16,916 --> 00:14:19,043
- 什么? - 我不放心
- What? - I'm not comfortable with this.

204
00:14:19,209 --> 00:14:20,920
- 爸爸 - 我了解这个世界 宝贝
- Dad. - I know the world, sweetie.

205
00:14:21,546 --> 00:14:24,256
- 爸爸 求你了 - 一个17岁的姑娘不该单独出行
- Dad, please. - A 17-year-old should not travel alone.

206
00:14:24,465 --> 00:14:26,676
- 我不是一个人啊 - 两个17岁的
- I'm not gonna be alone. - Two 17-year-olds.

207
00:14:26,842 --> 00:14:28,844
阿曼达19岁了
Amanda's 19.

208
00:14:34,433 --> 00:14:36,936
这样如何? 我和你们一起去?
How about this? How about if I go along?

209
00:14:37,144 --> 00:14:39,939
你们不会看到我的 我很擅长做隐形人
You won't know I'm there. I'm very good at being invisible.

210
00:14:40,147 --> 00:14:43,442
你就不能少操点心
As you so amply demonstrated for most of her life.

211
00:14:43,609 --> 00:14:45,194
签字吧 布莱恩
Just sign the paper, Bryan.

212
00:14:48,489 --> 00:14:49,615
我要想想
I'll think about it.

213
00:14:49,782 --> 00:14:51,951
我们都知道那表示什么
Everyone at this table knows what that means.

214
00:14:52,952 --> 00:14:55,412
嘿 金米 有件好事告诉你
Hey, Kimmy, there's something else.

215
00:14:56,205 --> 00:14:58,708
- 我不想听 - 金米
- I don't want anything else. - Kim.

216
00:15:05,339 --> 00:15:06,632
- 真搞不懂你 - 怎么?
- I don't get you. - What?

217
00:15:07,341 --> 00:15:10,135
为了国家你牺牲了我们的婚姻
You sacrificed our marriage in the service of the country.

218
00:15:10,302 --> 00:15:13,055
为了国家你把自己的生活搞得一团糟
You made a mess of your life in service of your country.

219
00:15:13,222 --> 00:15:16,058
这次你就不能为你女儿牺牲一点吗?
Can't you sacrifice a little this time for your daughter?

220
00:15:16,225 --> 00:15:19,103
- 我愿意为她牺牲一切 - 那到底是什么问题?
- I would sacrifice anything for her. - What's your problem?

221
00:15:19,269 --> 00:15:22,565
我不放心让女儿去冒险
I'm not comfortable putting my daughter at risk.

222
00:15:22,940 --> 00:15:26,736
去巴黎就是让女儿去冒险?
Putting our daughter at risk by going to Paris?

223
00:15:27,069 --> 00:15:29,154
你真可悲
You're pathetic.

224
00:15:44,587 --> 00:15:47,381
- 她来了 - 谢谢
- She's coming. - Thanks.

225
00:15:50,635 --> 00:15:51,677
三个条件
Three conditions.

226
00:15:52,011 --> 00:15:54,680
你住的地址和电话
The address and phone number of where you're staying.

227
00:15:54,847 --> 00:15:57,808
和谁出门 出门去哪里
You move, I wanna know where and with whom you'll be staying.

228
00:15:57,975 --> 00:16:01,521
到了给我打电话 每晚睡前给我打电话
Call me when you land. Call me every night before you go to sleep.

229
00:16:01,729 --> 00:16:03,481
这是全球漫游的 我的号码在里面
It's international. My number is in.

230
00:16:03,648 --> 00:16:05,775
- 好吧 真嗦 - 金米 你没在听
- Okay, awesome. - Kimmy, you're not focused.

231
00:16:05,941 --> 00:16:07,192
- 在听呀 - 我都说了什么?
- I am. - What did I say?

232
00:16:07,401 --> 00:16:10,696
你说到了给你打电话 每晚睡前给你打电话...
You said call you when I land, every night before I go to sleep...

233
00:16:10,905 --> 00:16:13,699
...你的手机是全球漫游的 你的号码就存在里面
...your phone's international, the number's programmed in.

234
00:16:13,908 --> 00:16:17,036
很好 最后一件事 我送你去机场
Okay, one last thing. I get to take you to the airport.

235
00:16:17,244 --> 00:16:18,704
好吧
Okay.

236
00:16:19,664 --> 00:16:21,499
- 拿去吧 - 耶
- There you go. - Yes.

237
00:16:21,666 --> 00:16:25,002
谢谢 爸爸 谢谢 谢谢 太谢谢了
Thank you, Daddy. Thank you, thank you, thank you.

238
00:16:25,169 --> 00:16:26,879
妈妈!
Mom!

239
00:16:28,923 --> 00:16:29,965
我爱你 爸爸
I love you, Dad.

240
00:16:30,800 --> 00:16:34,178
妈妈 他签了 他签了 我要去给阿曼达打电话!
Mom, he signed it, he signed it. I'm gonna go call Amanda!

241
00:16:37,973 --> 00:16:40,685
一开始就签了不就好了?
Wouldn't it have been easier to sign the first time?

242
00:16:40,851 --> 00:16:44,480
你跟我先谈下不更好?
Wouldn't it have been easier if you and I had talked about it first?

243
00:16:48,568 --> 00:16:51,654
在巴黎要注意的地方我都写下来了
Certain areas in Paris you should avoid. I've written them down.

244
00:16:51,821 --> 00:16:53,072
- 爸爸 - 来 拿去
- Dad. - Come on, take it.

245
00:16:53,238 --> 00:16:57,034
大部分时间我们都会在博物馆 别担心
We're gonna be spending 90 percent of our time in museums. Don't worry.

246
00:16:57,201 --> 00:16:59,912
就像说沾水不会弄湿一样 宝贝
That's like telling water not to be wet, sweetie.

247
00:17:00,370 --> 00:17:02,081
妈妈说你的工作让你神经质
Mom says your job made you paranoid.

248
00:17:02,289 --> 00:17:03,999
不 我的工作使我警觉
Well, my job made me aware.

249
00:17:05,751 --> 00:17:09,213
我以前总是问妈妈你是做什么的 为什么你老不在家
I used to ask Mom what your job was that you were away all the time.

250
00:17:09,379 --> 00:17:11,716
而她让我自己问你
And she would tell me to ask you.

251
00:17:11,882 --> 00:17:15,511
每次看到你 我都不敢问
Whenever I did see you, I was afraid to ask.

252
00:17:15,678 --> 00:17:17,429
是吗? 为什么呢?
Yeah? Why?

253
00:17:18,305 --> 00:17:21,100
不知道 也许是因为...
I don't know. Maybe because...

254
00:17:21,684 --> 00:17:23,936
...我害怕发现
...I was afraid to find out.

255
00:17:25,771 --> 00:17:27,940
也许是些我不喜欢的
Like, maybe it was something I wouldn't like.

256
00:17:28,524 --> 00:17:31,443
我为政府工作 你知道的
I worked for the government. You knew that.

257
00:17:31,944 --> 00:17:36,198
就像一个间谍 对吗?
So you were like a spy, right?

258
00:17:36,365 --> 00:17:39,827
- 如果我按下这个按钮会怎么样? - 别碰
- What happens if I push this button? - Don't touch that button.

259
00:17:40,536 --> 00:17:45,875
呃 不 事实上 我是... 我是负责防护工作的
Well, no, I was a... I was a preventer, actually.

260
00:17:46,041 --> 00:17:47,877
- 防护? - 是的
- A preventer? - Yeah.

261
00:17:48,503 --> 00:17:50,212
防护些什么?
What did you prevent?

262
00:17:50,379 --> 00:17:52,381
防止坏事发生
Bad things from happening.

263
00:17:52,840 --> 00:17:56,969
那是个好工作?
So it was a good job?

264
00:17:57,136 --> 00:17:59,930
对 是的
Yes. Yep, it was.

265
00:18:02,182 --> 00:18:03,893
你怀念它吗?
Do you miss it?

266
00:18:04,477 --> 00:18:05,728
我更想念你
I missed you more.

267
00:18:21,702 --> 00:18:23,120
- 金米! - 爸爸 是阿曼达
- Kim! - Dad, there's Amanda.

268
00:18:23,287 --> 00:18:25,122
去吧 我来拿包
Go ahead. I'll get the bags.

269
00:18:47,019 --> 00:18:49,522
- 金米会帮你拿的 - 我自己能行
- Jimmy'll give you a hand with those. - I can manage.

270
00:18:49,730 --> 00:18:51,148
勒诺
Lenore.

271
00:18:51,315 --> 00:18:54,151
你知道吗? 她不仅仅去巴黎
Do you know about this? She's not just going to Paris.

272
00:18:54,944 --> 00:18:56,487
- 我知道 - 她对我撒谎
- I know. - She lied to me.

273
00:18:56,654 --> 00:18:58,823
是的 因为她没法对你说实情
Yes, because she can't be honest with you.

274
00:18:59,490 --> 00:19:01,033
为什么? 什么意思?
Why? What are you talking about?

275
00:19:01,241 --> 00:19:02,868
你老说规矩啊条件啊
Your rules and conditions.

276
00:19:03,077 --> 00:19:04,369
这是什么?
What is this?

277
00:19:04,537 --> 00:19:07,289
U2的欧洲巡演日程
It's U2's European tour dates.

278
00:19:07,457 --> 00:19:09,459
她要跟随一个摇滚乐队环游欧洲?
She's following a rock band around Europe?

279
00:19:09,625 --> 00:19:13,337
孩子们都这样 斯图尔特帮她搞到了票 为她安排了最好的酒店
All kids do. Stuart got her tickets, arranged her to stay in the best hotels.

280
00:19:13,504 --> 00:19:16,674
最好的酒店 知道吗 你住在自己的小圈子里...
Best hotels. You know, you live in your little bubble here...

281
00:19:16,841 --> 00:19:20,219
...有仆人和司机供差遣
...behind your wall, with your maids and chauffeurs and servants.

282
00:19:20,385 --> 00:19:21,846
根本不知道外面的真实世界
No idea what the world is like.

283
00:19:22,054 --> 00:19:25,850
是的 可她也不知道 所以才要出去体验一下
Yes, and neither will she unless she goes out and experiences it.

284
00:19:28,102 --> 00:19:29,979
不要说我不懂这个世界
Don't tell me I don't know the world.

285
00:19:30,145 --> 00:19:34,108
五年来我一直在等你的电话 你总是好几周都不打回来
For five years I waited for a phone call that didn't come for weeks at a time.

286
00:19:34,274 --> 00:19:37,319
我总是担心会有人敲门 告诉我你已经死了
For a knock on the door telling me there'd be no calls anymore.

287
00:19:41,532 --> 00:19:45,536
听着 我知道你搬来这 是为了重建你和金米的关系
Listen, I know you moved here to build some sort of relationship with Kimmy.

288
00:19:45,703 --> 00:19:48,539
但你不能这样管着她
But you're not gonna do that by smothering her.

289
00:19:48,706 --> 00:19:52,251
让她去吧 否则我肯定 我肯定你会失去她
Let her live, or I promise, I promise you'll lose her.

290
00:19:59,258 --> 00:20:00,259
姑娘们
Girls.

291
00:20:05,931 --> 00:20:07,099
金米!
Kim!

292
00:20:13,063 --> 00:20:14,106
我爱你们
I love you.

293
00:20:15,983 --> 00:20:18,277
走吧 走
Let's go. Come on.

294
00:20:30,372 --> 00:20:32,249
我会教你法语
I'll teach you the French words I know.

295
00:20:32,416 --> 00:20:34,960
- 我会的也不多 但是... - 好的 太棒了
- Which may not be that much, but... - Okay. Yeah, right.

296
00:20:39,965 --> 00:20:41,967
三 好了 照张...
Three. Okay, now take one...

297
00:20:42,176 --> 00:20:44,136
要帮忙吗? 帮你们俩合影?
Need some help? One with the two of you?

298
00:20:44,679 --> 00:20:46,639
好的 谢谢
Yes, please.

299
00:20:46,806 --> 00:20:48,808
- 好了 - 他长得真不错
- Okay. - He's really cute.

300
00:20:49,016 --> 00:20:51,769
好了 不错 很漂亮
Okay. Yeah, great. Very nice.

301
00:20:51,936 --> 00:20:52,978
你们从哪来的?
Where are you from?

302
00:20:53,479 --> 00:20:55,189
加利福尼亚
California.

303
00:21:01,070 --> 00:21:02,154
我叫彼得
No. I'm Peter.

304
00:21:07,993 --> 00:21:09,829
- 这是金米 - 你好
- This is Kim. - Hi.

305
00:21:09,995 --> 00:21:11,163
- 很高兴见到你 - 你好
- Nice to meet you. - Hi.

306
00:21:11,330 --> 00:21:12,790
嗨
Hey.

307
00:21:12,957 --> 00:21:15,417
你们要去巴黎?
You're going into Paris?

308
00:21:16,085 --> 00:21:18,546
你们知道 这的出租车贵的要死
You know, taxis here are so damned expensive.

309
00:21:18,713 --> 00:21:19,839
一起搭车如何?
Want to share?

310
00:21:20,047 --> 00:21:21,841
- 好的 当然可以 - 太好了
- Yeah. Sure. - Okay, perfect.

311
00:21:22,007 --> 00:21:23,843
谢谢
Thanks.

312
00:21:25,385 --> 00:21:28,973
查询航班抵达 请按1
To check arrivals, please press one.

313
00:21:29,139 --> 00:21:31,642
请输入航班
Please enter the flight number.

314
00:21:33,811 --> 00:21:37,189
288号航班在当地时间上午8点...
Flight 288 arrived in Paris Charles de Gaulle...

315
00:21:37,356 --> 00:21:40,860
...抵达巴黎戴高乐机场
...at 8 a.m. Local time.

316
00:21:42,111 --> 00:21:43,529
耶
Yeah.

317
00:21:43,696 --> 00:21:46,156
哦 不是真的吧?
Oh, are you serious?

318
00:21:46,365 --> 00:21:48,659
- 哦 我的天 - 这地方真不错
