给你外套的那个女孩在房子里吗?
The girl who gave you this, was she in the house?

637
00:57:11,824 --> 00:57:13,451
她是好人
She was nice.

638
00:57:13,618 --> 00:57:15,119
我知道
I know.

639
00:57:16,120 --> 00:57:17,580
她是我女儿
She's my daughter.

640
00:57:22,752 --> 00:57:25,463
我必须找到那座房子 你知道在哪吗?
I need to find this house. Do you know where it is?

641
00:57:32,261 --> 00:57:33,303
天堂
Paradise.

642
00:57:49,444 --> 00:57:51,113
- 早上好 - 有事吗?
- Good morning. - May I help you?

643
00:57:51,280 --> 00:57:53,407
- 我要见你们老板 - 老板不在
- I'm here to see your boss. - No boss.

644
00:57:58,954 --> 00:58:01,040
我们没做什么非法的事
We're doing nothing wrong here.

645
00:58:02,458 --> 00:58:04,376
按一下 30个特工就会出现在这...
One button, and 30 agents will be here...

646
00:58:04,544 --> 00:58:06,837
...你们根本没时间卷铺盖走人
...before you have time to scratch your balls.

647
00:58:07,046 --> 00:58:10,299
别耍人了 再浪费我时间 小心我干掉你
Stop jerking around before I close you down for wasting my time.

648
00:58:16,055 --> 00:58:17,515
在这等着
Wait here.

649
00:58:30,319 --> 00:58:31,320
你带着武器?
You have weapon?

650
00:58:31,904 --> 00:58:32,947
你手上拿着呢
You're holding it.

651
00:59:01,517 --> 00:59:03,018
黑咖啡 一块糖 谢谢
Black, one sugar, please.

652
00:59:10,234 --> 00:59:11,360
你要什么?
What is it you want?

653
00:59:12,903 --> 00:59:14,530
我是来谈价钱的
I'm here to negotiate the rates.

654
00:59:14,697 --> 00:59:17,908
我们和梅肯先生谈过了
We already negotiated the rate with Mr. Macon.

655
00:59:18,117 --> 00:59:21,245
梅肯先生调到别的区了
Mr. Macon has moved to another division.

656
00:59:21,454 --> 00:59:23,247
我是来重新谈的
I'm here for the renegotiation.

657
00:59:27,126 --> 00:59:30,713
觉得我有道理的话 那我接着说了
Unless you think I'm being unreasonable, let me explain ourselves.

658
00:59:31,547 --> 00:59:35,760
咖啡不错 我们利用卫星全天24小时监视你们
Nice coffee. We have you under satellite surveillance, 24 hours a day.

659
00:59:35,968 --> 00:59:39,597
你们说的每句话 做的每件事 我们都知道
We hear everything you say, we know everything you do.

660
00:59:39,764 --> 00:59:43,100
你知不知道 光是改变地球上空200米...
Do you have any idea what it costs just to change the angle...

661
00:59:43,267 --> 00:59:46,729
...轨道卫星的镜头角度 就要花多少钱?
...of the lens on a satellite orbiting 200 miles above the Earth?

662
00:59:47,104 --> 00:59:48,481
而且价格还在上涨
And those costs have gone up.

663
00:59:48,648 --> 00:59:51,901
我们的费用上涨 随之你们的费用也得上涨 再正常不过了
Our costs go up, your costs go up. It's only logical.

664
00:59:52,818 --> 00:59:55,154
另外 你们谁是马科?
By the way, which one of you is Marko?

665
00:59:55,320 --> 00:59:57,114
你问这干嘛?
Why do you want to know?

666
00:59:57,322 --> 00:59:58,824
我听说马科是这的老大
I was told Marko is in charge.

667
00:59:59,033 --> 01:00:00,785
我们都是马科
We are all Marko.

668
01:00:01,786 --> 01:00:03,412
马科来自卓帕加
Marko from Tropoja.

669
01:00:03,579 --> 01:00:04,830
我们都来自卓帕加
We are all from Tropoja.

670
01:00:07,625 --> 01:00:10,961
如果你们那么想玩游戏 那么费用上升10%
If that's the game you want to play, the rate just went up 10 percent.

671
01:00:11,128 --> 01:00:15,340
不要以为我们是移民就可以敲诈我们 我们懂法律
If you are trying to extort us because we are immigrants, we know the law.

672
01:00:15,758 --> 01:00:18,260
我敲诈你们是因为你们做了违法的事
I'm extorting you because you are breaking the law.

673
01:00:18,427 --> 01:00:20,930
你们喜欢以哪项罪名被捕?
Which charge would you like to be arrested for?

674
01:00:21,096 --> 01:00:24,099
贩毒 绑架 卖淫? 随你们挑
Drugs, kidnapping, prostitution? Take your pick.

675
01:00:24,308 --> 01:00:26,852
你们来到这个国家 利用这个国家...
You come to this country, take advantage of it...

676
01:00:27,061 --> 01:00:30,105
...我们宽容并不代表我们懦弱无助
...and think because we are tolerant, we are weak and helpless.

677
01:00:30,523 --> 01:00:32,149
你们的傲慢无礼激怒了我
Your arrogance offends me.

678
01:00:32,357 --> 01:00:34,318
为此 费用提升10%
For that, the rate went up 10 percent.

679
01:00:35,528 --> 01:00:38,614
现在 你们要谈正事还是继续玩?
Now, do you want to get down to business or to keep playing?

680
01:00:40,575 --> 01:00:42,367
- 多少? - 20%
- How much? - Twenty percent.

681
01:00:42,577 --> 01:00:45,329
而且我保证一年内不会上涨
And you have my word it'll not go up for a year.

682
01:00:54,338 --> 01:00:57,467
用你们的语言如何说"糖"?
How do you say "sugar" in your language?

683
01:01:10,813 --> 01:01:13,023
你们做了明智的决定 先生们
You've made a very good investment, gentlemen.

684
01:01:13,232 --> 01:01:14,358
一个月后见
See you in a month.

685
01:01:19,321 --> 01:01:22,492
一个朋友给我的 是阿尔巴尼亚语 不介意翻一下吧?
A friend gave this to me. It's Albanian. You mind translating it?

686
01:01:34,837 --> 01:01:36,506
祝你好运
Good luck.

687
01:01:36,922 --> 01:01:38,048
- 祝你好运 - 祝你好运
- Good luck. - Good luck.

688
01:01:38,841 --> 01:01:40,635
- 祝你好运 祝你好运 - 祝你好运
- Good luck. Good luck. - Good luck.

689
01:01:50,520 --> 01:01:52,229
你不记得我了
You don't remember me.

690
01:01:53,022 --> 01:01:55,024
两天前我们通过电话
We spoke on the phone two days ago.

691
01:01:58,569 --> 01:02:00,029
我告诉过你我会找到你
I told you I would find you.

692
01:03:05,010 --> 01:03:06,095
金米
Kim.

693
01:03:20,442 --> 01:03:22,027
阿曼达
Amanda.

694
01:03:57,980 --> 01:03:59,023
醒醒!
Wake up!

695
01:03:59,565 --> 01:04:01,316
我要你集中精神
I need you to be focused.

696
01:04:04,487 --> 01:04:06,363
精神集中了吗?
Are you focused yet?

697
01:04:16,206 --> 01:04:17,374
这女孩在哪?
Where is this girl?

698
01:04:18,000 --> 01:04:19,710
她在哪?
Where is she?

699
01:04:48,280 --> 01:04:52,076
你知道 我们以前会外包这种事
You know, we used to outsource this kind of thing.

700
01:04:52,284 --> 01:04:54,912
但我们发现 我们外包的那些国家...
But what we found was the countries we outsourced to...

701
01:04:55,079 --> 01:04:58,458
...电网都不怎么稳定 典型的第三世界
...had unreliable power grids. Very Third World.

702
01:04:58,624 --> 01:05:00,960
你按了开关 却没有电...
You'd turn on a switch, power wouldn't come on...

703
01:05:01,126 --> 01:05:05,130
...真是气死人 没办法 就只能拔指甲
...and then tempers would get short. People would resort to pulling fingernails.

704
01:05:05,339 --> 01:05:07,633
在裸露的皮肤上洒酸溶液
Acid drips on bare skin.

705
01:05:07,842 --> 01:05:10,260
这些只会造成反效果
The whole exercise would become counterproductive.

706
01:05:10,427 --> 01:05:12,096
但在这里 电力很稳定
But here, the power's stable.

707
01:05:12,262 --> 01:05:14,599
这里的电流源源不断
Here, there's a nice even flow.

708
01:05:14,765 --> 01:05:18,060
轻按开关 电力就能持续一整天
Here, you can flip a switch and the power stays on all day.

709
01:05:22,147 --> 01:05:23,483
她在哪?
Where is she?

710
01:05:44,419 --> 01:05:48,382
我可没什么时间可以浪费 卓帕加的马科
Now, I don't have any more time to waste, Marko from Tropoja.

711
01:05:48,841 --> 01:05:51,135
回答我 否则这个开关会一直开着...
Give me what I need or this switch'll stay on...

712
01:05:51,301 --> 01:05:54,263
...直到他们付不出电费而关掉
...till they turn power off for lack of payment on the bill.

713
01:05:55,515 --> 01:05:56,807
我女儿在哪?
Where is my daughter?

714
01:05:57,349 --> 01:06:00,770
我们不会留着处女 我们会卖了她们
We don't keep virgins, we sell them.

715
01:06:01,020 --> 01:06:03,147
她是处女 可以卖一大笔
She was virgin, lot of money.

716
01:06:03,355 --> 01:06:05,483
你把我女儿卖了? 你把她卖了?
You sold my daughter? You sold her?

717
01:06:07,527 --> 01:06:09,153
卖给谁了?
To who?

718
01:06:09,862 --> 01:06:11,489
我不知道
I don't know.

719
01:06:13,949 --> 01:06:15,826
- 什么? - 圣・嘉力
- What? - Saint-Clair.

720
01:06:16,326 --> 01:06:17,327
圣・嘉力
Saint-Clair.

721
01:06:17,787 --> 01:06:20,330
圣・嘉力? 圣・嘉力 是个人 还是个地方?
Saint-Clair? Saint-Clair. Is that a person, a place?

722
01:06:21,957 --> 01:06:24,960
是个人 帕特里斯・圣・嘉力
Person. Patrice Saint-Clair.

723
01:06:25,169 --> 01:06:26,170
帕特里斯・圣・嘉力
Patrice Saint-Clair.

724
01:06:27,379 --> 01:06:28,673
在哪能找到他?
Where can I find him?

725
01:06:29,674 --> 01:06:31,509
我不知道 我不知道
I don't know, I don't know.

726
01:06:32,301 --> 01:06:35,012
我不知道 我不知道 我不知道
I don't know. I don't know. I don't know.

727
01:06:35,220 --> 01:06:37,473
求求你! 我真的不知道!
Please! I don't know!

728
01:06:37,640 --> 01:06:41,644
我不知道! 不! 求求你! 求求你
I don't know! No! Please! Please.

729
01:06:41,811 --> 01:06:43,646
求求你
Please.

730
01:06:43,813 --> 01:06:45,898
不要 求求你
Not that. Please.

731
01:06:46,065 --> 01:06:47,483
我相信你
I believe you.

732
01:06:50,319 --> 01:06:52,572
但我不能放过你
But it's not gonna save you.

733
01:07:15,761 --> 01:07:17,597
看看谁来了
Look who dropped by.

734
01:07:18,430 --> 01:07:21,016
布莱恩 真是意外啊
Bryan, what a pleasant surprise.

735
01:07:21,225 --> 01:07:22,226
吉恩・克劳德
Jean-Claude.

736
01:07:22,434 --> 01:07:24,895
孩子们在等你
The children waited up for you.

737
01:07:25,062 --> 01:07:28,398
快带他们去睡觉 我们还能吃顿热乎乎的
If you tuck them in, maybe we can eat before everything gets cold.

738
01:07:28,566 --> 01:07:30,067
布莱恩 来帮下忙?
Bryan, will you do the honors?

739
01:07:30,275 --> 01:07:32,194
- 好的 - 我马上来
- Sure. - I'll be just a minute.

740
01:08:02,725 --> 01:08:04,894
我正跟布莱恩说 你换了新工作后...
I was just telling Bryan how nice it's been...

741
01:08:05,060 --> 01:08:07,229
...一切变得好多了
...since you left the old job for the new one.

742
01:08:07,396 --> 01:08:10,232
每晚回家吃饭 见到孩子们的时间也多了
Home every night for dinner, get to see the kids more.

743
01:08:10,399 --> 01:08:13,443
每晚回家 看着孩子们 一定很幸福
Yeah, must be nice coming home every night, seeing your kids.

744
01:08:13,653 --> 01:08:15,738
布莱恩在考虑搬家
Bryan has been thinking about relocating.

745
01:08:16,155 --> 01:08:17,615
- 真的? - 是的
- Really? - Yes.

746
01:08:17,823 --> 01:08:19,617
搬到巴黎 他在看房子了
To Paris, he's been visiting houses.

747
01:08:19,784 --> 01:08:22,453
- 要鸡胸还鸡腿? - 鸡腿 谢谢
- White or dark meat? - Dark, please.

748
01:08:22,620 --> 01:08:23,954
有看上的吗?
Find anything interesting?

749
01:08:24,121 --> 01:08:27,917
说实话 有啊 在天堂街第十区
As a matter of fact, I did, in the 10th arrondissement on Rue Paradis.

750
01:08:28,834 --> 01:08:31,295
住那的人认识你的一个同事
People there know someone that works in your office.

751
01:08:31,546 --> 01:08:33,506
一位梅肯先生 你认识吗?
A Mr. Macon. Do you know him?

752
01:08:33,673 --> 01:08:35,966
哦 亨利 我都叫他紧张先生
Oh, Henry. I call him Mr. Nervous.

753
01:08:36,133 --> 01:08:39,804
总是一副会有麻烦的样子 要胡萝卜吗?
Always seems like he's about to have a problem. Carrots?

754
01:08:40,012 --> 01:08:41,806
我查到了 吉恩・克劳德
I got to the bottom of it, Jean-Claude.

755
01:08:42,181 --> 01:08:43,307
我什么都知道了
I know everything.

756
01:08:44,058 --> 01:08:46,310
我希望你没趟进这浑水
I hope you're not involved in this shit.

757
01:08:47,687 --> 01:08:50,523
- 什么浑水? - 现在不该说这些 布莱恩
- What shit? - This is not the time or place, Bryan.

758
01:08:50,690 --> 01:08:52,775
- 你掺合进来了? - 掺合进什么?
- Are you involved? - Involved in what?

759
01:08:53,442 --> 01:08:54,944
你们俩在说什么?
What are you two talking about?

760
01:08:55,110 --> 01:08:58,698
- 是不是? - 我的薪水是X 我的开支是Y
- Are you? - My salary is X, my expenses are Y.

761
01:08:58,864 --> 01:09:00,950
只要能养家...
As long as my family is provided for...

762
01:09:01,116 --> 01:09:03,703
...我不在乎从哪弄钱
...I do not care where the difference comes from.

763
01:09:03,869 --> 01:09:05,788
我就是那样卷进来的
That is my entire involvement.

764
01:09:05,955 --> 01:09:07,957
- 那我的家人呢? - 我告诉你...
- What about my family? - I told you...

765
01:09:08,123 --> 01:09:10,543
...只要不惹麻烦 我会帮你的
...I would help as long as it didn't cause trouble.

766
01:09:10,710 --> 01:09:12,044
谁是帕特里斯・圣・嘉力?
Who is Patrice Saint-Clair?

767
01:09:12,211 --> 01:09:15,715
我不知道 我也不关心 我载你去机场
I don't know, I don't care. I am driving you to the airport.

768
01:09:15,965 --> 01:09:17,174
吉恩・克劳德
Jean-Claude.

769
01:09:18,676 --> 01:09:20,344
走吧 晚餐结束了
Let's get going. Dinner is over.

770
01:09:20,511 --> 01:09:22,304
- 我还没吃完 - 不 你吃完了
- I'm not finished yet. - Yes, you are.

771
01:09:22,555 --> 01:09:25,390
- 不! - 不 我还没有
- No! - No, I'm not.

772
01:09:30,145 --> 01:09:33,357
那就是你做文职的后果 你忘了些事
That's what happens when you sit behind a desk. You forget things.

773
01:09:33,566 --> 01:09:36,026
就如你都忘了 上了弹的枪拿在手上的重量
Like the weight in the hand of a gun that's loaded.

774
01:09:38,112 --> 01:09:39,238
伊莎贝尔!
Isabelle!

775
01:09:40,698 --> 01:09:41,866
只是皮肉伤
It's a flesh wound.

776
01:09:42,032 --> 01:09:45,703
但你再不说 就会看到你最不想看的...
But if you don't get me what I need, the last thing you'll see...

777
01:09:45,911 --> 01:09:47,872
...我会射穿她的脑门
...is the bullet I put between her eyes.

778
01:09:48,080 --> 01:09:51,125
现在 告诉我谁是帕特里斯・圣・嘉力
Now, Patrice Saint-Clair.

779
01:10:02,762 --> 01:10:04,555
你本可以少受点苦...
You could've made this less painful...

780
01:10:04,722 --> 01:10:08,851
...只要你多关心点我女儿 而不是你的职位
...if you had been more concerned about my daughter and less about your desk.

781
01:10:09,018 --> 01:10:11,353
请替我向你妻子道歉
Please apologize to your wife for me.

782
01:11:16,627 --> 01:11:19,464
- 能为您效劳吗? - 我来找圣・嘉力先生
- Can I help you? - Yes, I'm here to see Mr. Saint-Clair.

783
01:11:19,672 --> 01:11:21,215
请告诉我您的名字
Your name, please.

784
01:11:25,219 --> 01:11:27,137
抱歉 上面没有您的名字
I'm sorry, your name is not on the list.

785
01:11:27,304 --> 01:11:28,848
哦 请再检查一次
Oh, please check again.

786
01:11:31,934 --> 01:11:33,644
进去
Inside.

787
01:12:21,275 --> 01:12:22,527
需要帮忙吗 先生?
May I help you, sir?

788
01:12:28,157 --> 01:12:30,660
- 您点的香槟 - 没错 放这吧
- Your champagne. - Yeah, I will take it.

789
01:12:40,419 --> 01:12:43,714
现在出价5万 5万
I have 50,000. Fifty thousand.

790
01:12:45,508 --> 01:12:47,510
5万
Fifty thousand.

791
01:12:49,094 --> 01:12:52,347
10万 10万
One hundred, 100,000.

792
01:12:54,183 --> 01:12:57,352
10万 15万
One hundred, 150.

793
01:12:58,437 --> 01:12:59,605
现在出价15万
I have 150.

794
01:13:00,272 --> 01:13:02,399
您的香槟 先生
Your champagne, sir.

795
01:13:03,192 --> 01:13:05,903
20万 现在出价20万 25万
Two, I have two, 250.

796
01:13:06,070 --> 01:13:07,071
要为您倒酒吗?
May I serve?

797
01:13:07,279 --> 01:13:08,614
- 谢谢 - 现在出价25万
- Please. - I have 250.

798
01:13:10,449 --> 01:13:12,201
25万
Two-fifty.

799
01:13:12,785 --> 01:13:15,830
25万成交
Sold for 250,000.

800
01:13:33,889 --> 01:13:36,058
最后一件拍品
The last item.

801
01:13:36,391 --> 01:13:38,894
惯例 最好的留到最后
As usual, we save the best for last.

802
01:13:39,228 --> 01:13:41,396
说英语 会一点法语
Speaks English, some French.

803
01:13:41,564 --> 01:13:42,982
绝对是处女
Certified pure.

804
01:13:52,950 --> 01:13:53,951
- 对不起 - 出去
- Sorry. - Get out.

805
01:13:55,578 --> 01:13:58,288
起价为10万
The bidding will begin at 100,000.

806
01:14:01,792 --> 01:14:03,919
10万
